name: Dominique Provost-Chalkley
description:
Requested by @Zorglub!

Dominique Provost-Chalkley is a British-Canadian actress, activist and songwriter best known for playing as Waverly Earp in the supernatural Western horror Wynonna Earp. Dominique also played the role of Zrinka in Avengers: Age of Ultron.

As usual, the embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models for which it has been tested. There is a chance that Stable Diffusion makes something weird of the nosebridge, it shouldn't happen often but if it does, changing the sampling steps or inpainting will fix it.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
